Puppet module: manhunt

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages manhunt software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include manhunt              # Install and run manhunt with standard configurations.
include manhunt::disable     # Disable manhunt service.
include manhunt::disableboot # Disable manhunt service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include manhunt::absent      # Remove manhunt package.

DEPENDENCIES:
